                <note rend="inline" type="source">500.A15A4 Steering Committee/502: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Switzerland</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Wilson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bern</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1937-01-26T18:00:00+01:00"
                            >January 26, 1937—6 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received January 26—2 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>11. In this afternoon’s session the Council fixed May 6th for the meeting of the
                    Bureau of the Disarmament Conference.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
